# Running Tests

Always run tests with `--noinput` to suppress the "destroy existing test database?" prompt:

```bash
python manage.py test --settings=example_app.settings_ci --noinput
```

Run from `example_app/` using the project `.venv`:

```bash
cd example_app && ../.venv/bin/python manage.py test --settings=example_app.settings_ci --noinput
```
